   {
      "author_association" : "MEMBER",
      "body" : "I think there are two solutions:\r\n\r\n* Keep the code as-is, and document why the `unsigned`->`signed` conversion is intended\r\n* Make compressor throw directly instead of calling `s.ignore(nSize)` (and hoping for a throw), when `nSize` is larger than the maximum block size or so. ",
